text: Police in a Detroit suburb stumbled onto an insane discovery recently when they charged a man for stealing pills from the CVS pharmacy where he worked. The man was Leonard Rayne Moses, a convicted killer who’d been on the lam for nearly five decades. https://t.co/wtTwAZJkiH
